49:57.000 --> 50:01.000
If the enterprise receives a discount

50:01.000 --> 50:05.000
depending on the volume of the purchase

50:05.000 --> 50:09.000
the more the volume of the purchase

50:09.000 --> 50:13.000
the more discount the partner receives.

50:13.000 --> 50:17.000
Thus, discounts are used

50:17.000 --> 50:21.000
to increase the volume of the production.

50:21.000 --> 50:25.000
The use of discounts leads to the increase

50:25.000 --> 50:29.000
of the volume of the production and the increase of the debt.

50:29.000 --> 50:33.000
With the help of discounts

50:33.000 --> 50:37.000
the debt can be regulated.

50:37.000 --> 50:41.000
We want to increase the debt

50:41.000 --> 50:45.000
and we want to use it as a tool.

50:45.000 --> 50:49.000
Thus, we should look at the discounts.

50:49.000 --> 50:53.000
Using the discount mechanism

