51:25.000 --> 51:29.000
Even a short-term loan takes time.

51:29.000 --> 51:33.000
And the money needs to be fast.

51:33.000 --> 51:37.000
So, discounts are used.

51:37.000 --> 51:41.000
The discount mechanism is used

51:41.000 --> 51:45.000
to increase the volume of the production

51:45.000 --> 51:49.000
and to get additional money for the enterprise.

51:49.000 --> 51:53.000
Discounts can also be used

51:53.000 --> 51:57.000
instead of fines.

51:57.000 --> 52:01.000
In fact, usually, the contract

52:01.000 --> 52:05.000
uses a combination of the loan

52:05.000 --> 52:09.000
and the debt.

52:09.000 --> 52:13.000
But, as practice has shown,

52:13.000 --> 52:17.000
it's not the most effective way

52:17.000 --> 52:21.000
to manage the debt.

52:21.000 --> 52:25.000
There is a more effective way.

52:25.000 --> 52:29.000
The enterprise gets an additional discount

52:29.000 --> 52:33.000
if it returns the money

52:33.000 --> 52:37.000
before the contract expires.

52:37.000 --> 52:41.000
So, the contract says

52:41.000 --> 52:45.000
