52:45.000 --> 52:49.000
If the money is not returned in 30 days,

52:49.000 --> 52:53.000
there will be fines of the same amount.

52:53.000 --> 52:57.000
And there is an additional condition.

52:57.000 --> 53:01.000
If the enterprise returns the money

53:01.000 --> 53:05.000
before the contract expires,

53:05.000 --> 53:09.000
it will get a discount on the product

53:09.000 --> 53:13.000
it purchased.

53:13.000 --> 53:17.000
This is the most effective way

53:17.000 --> 53:21.000
to pay off the debt.

53:21.000 --> 53:25.000
Because the enterprise

53:25.000 --> 53:29.000
wants to reduce the costs

53:29.000 --> 53:33.000
of the company's financial policy

53:33.000 --> 53:37.000
and to pay off the debt in advance.

53:37.000 --> 53:41.000
And to get additional discounts

53:41.000 --> 53:45.000
on the product it has already purchased.

53:45.000 --> 53:49.000
In this case, the enterprise

53:49.000 --> 53:53.000
that provides such a discount is profitable.

53:53.000 --> 53:57.000
But, again, we should compare

53:57.000 --> 54:01.000
the benefits of the discount

54:01.000 --> 54:05.000
with the benefits of the loan.

54:05.000 --> 54:09.000
Should the enterprise use the money

54:09.000 --> 54:13.000
to get additional profit

54:13.000 --> 54:17.000
or leave it as a loan

54:17.000 --> 54:21.000
to the consumer?

54:21.000 --> 54:25.000
If the enterprise's own consumption

54:25.000 --> 54:29.000
is more effective than the interest

54:29.000 --> 54:33.000
you will have to pay

54:33.000 --> 54:37.000
for the money you will get in advance.

54:37.000 --> 54:41.000
For example, if your business's profitability

54:41.000 --> 54:45.000
is 40% per month,

54:45.000 --> 54:49.000
and you will get a 1% discount

54:49.000 --> 54:53.000
for the money you will get in half a month,

54:53.000 --> 54:57.000
you will get a 1% discount.

54:57.000 --> 55:01.000
Because you will create more profit

55:01.000 --> 55:05.000
in your own business

55:05.000 --> 55:09.000
than if you leave the money

55:09.000 --> 55:13.000
with the enterprise.

55:13.000 --> 55:17.000
And the enterprise that takes the loan

55:17.000 --> 55:21.000
can have a month's discount

55:21.000 --> 55:25.000
and you will pay it in advance.

55:25.000 --> 55:29.000
You just give it an additional opportunity.

55:29.000 --> 55:33.000
And then the enterprise decides

55:33.000 --> 55:37.000
what is more profitable for it.

55:37.000 --> 55:41.000
So, practice has shown that using

55:41.000 --> 55:45.000
such a mechanism in business

55:45.000 --> 55:49.000
is the most effective way

55:49.000 --> 55:53.000
to get a discount.

55:53.000 --> 55:57.000
So, take this information

55:57.000 --> 56:01.000
and try to use this mechanism

56:01.000 --> 56:05.000
in your contracts.

56:05.000 --> 56:09.000
I think you will find it very useful.

56:09.000 --> 56:13.000
Besides the discounts I suggest you use,

56:13.000 --> 56:17.000
you can use other mechanisms

56:17.000 --> 56:21.000
that are not actively used.

56:21.000 --> 56:25.000
This is a mechanism of imposing fines

56:25.000 --> 56:29.000
for the delay of payment.

56:29.000 --> 56:33.000
The fine should be such

56:33.000 --> 56:37.000
that it is more profitable to return it

56:37.000 --> 56:41.000
than to pay the fine.

56:41.000 --> 56:45.000
Many enterprises do not write down

56:45.000 --> 56:49.000
the sanctions,

56:49.000 --> 56:53.000
because they forget

56:53.000 --> 56:57.000
that they have to return the loan.

56:57.000 --> 57:01.000
And this is a very long process.

57:01.000 --> 57:05.000
There are many cases

57:05.000 --> 57:09.000
when the loan was withdrawn

57:09.000 --> 57:13.000
for a month.

57:13.000 --> 57:17.000
And there were no sanctions.

57:17.000 --> 57:21.000
The most friendly relations

57:21.000 --> 57:25.000
were returned years later.

57:25.000 --> 57:29.000
Of course, there were no additional

57:29.000 --> 57:33.000
compensations in the absence of sanctions.

57:33.000 --> 57:37.000
At least the amount that was presented

