as a commodity loan was returned.

57:41.000 --> 57:45.000
But this is not profitable

57:45.000 --> 57:49.000
for the enterprise.

57:49.000 --> 57:53.000
Because money withdrawn

57:53.000 --> 57:57.000
does not bring any additional income

57:57.000 --> 58:01.000
to the company.

58:01.000 --> 58:05.000
The presence of a fine

58:05.000 --> 58:09.000
will protect you

58:09.000 --> 58:13.000
from the sanctions.

58:13.000 --> 58:17.000
But if you do not want to quarrel,

58:17.000 --> 58:21.000
but want to live in friendly relations,

58:21.000 --> 58:25.000
then you can use another way

58:25.000 --> 58:29.000
