59:01.000 --> 59:05.000
This way you have secured yourself.

59:05.000 --> 59:09.000
You have received the loan and you are paid.

59:09.000 --> 59:13.000
Instead of seeking a return

59:13.000 --> 59:17.000
of the loan, you just provide Vexel

59:17.000 --> 59:21.000
and get the payment.

59:21.000 --> 59:25.000
This is also a very effective mechanism.

59:25.000 --> 59:29.000
The next mechanism is used

59:29.000 --> 59:33.000
when you do not know the business partner

59:33.000 --> 59:37.000
and do not give the commodity you produced.

59:37.000 --> 59:41.000
You just do not give it to the lender

59:41.000 --> 59:45.000
but sell it on prepayment.

59:45.000 --> 59:49.000
Remember, I already told you today

59:49.000 --> 59:53.000
that in the early 90s all foreign companies

59:53.000 --> 59:57.000
provided commodities for Russian businessmen.

