You do not have to give prepayment.

01:00:33.000 --> 01:00:37.000
The last mechanism

01:00:37.000 --> 01:00:41.000
that can be used to speed up the return

01:00:41.000 --> 01:00:45.000
of the debit debt is the factoring mechanism.

01:00:45.000 --> 01:00:49.000
I have already mentioned that factoring

01:00:49.000 --> 01:00:53.000
is a modern, new, growing mechanism

01:00:53.000 --> 01:00:57.000
for the return of all kinds of debts

01:00:57.000 --> 01:01:01.000
that are in front of the company.

01:01:01.000 --> 01:01:05.000
For example, the debt of the debitor.

01:01:05.000 --> 01:01:09.000
You provide the commodity in the form of a credit

01:01:09.000 --> 01:01:13.000
and sign a triple contract

01:01:13.000 --> 01:01:17.000
where the third party is the factoring company

01:01:17.000 --> 01:01:21.000
and you provide all the documents

01:01:21.000 --> 01:01:25.000
about the return of the commodity.

01:01:25.000 --> 01:01:29.000
The debt is not paid in full,

01:01:29.000 --> 01:01:33.000
usually it is paid in 90%.

01:01:33.000 --> 01:01:37.000
This way the mechanism of factoring

01:01:37.000 --> 01:01:41.000
has an economic basis

01:01:41.000 --> 01:01:45.000
and does not contain the mechanism

01:01:45.000 --> 01:01:49.000
of pumping money from the bank.

01:01:49.000 --> 01:01:53.000
The economic mechanism was not a lie.

01:01:53.000 --> 01:01:57.000
Factoring companies are developing rapidly.

01:01:57.000 --> 01:02:01.000
It is very profitable to use factoring business

01:02:01.000 --> 01:02:05.000
for the enterprises that are engaged in production.

01:02:05.000 --> 01:02:09.000
Moreover, factoring companies

01:02:09.000 --> 01:02:13.000
not only provide money,

01:02:13.000 --> 01:02:17.000
they also perform other additional functions.

01:02:17.000 --> 01:02:21.000
For example, they can track the return

01:02:21.000 --> 01:02:25.000
of the debt of the debitor.

01:02:25.000 --> 01:02:29.000
Moreover, factoring companies

01:02:29.000 --> 01:02:33.000
ensure the non-return of the debt of the debitor.

01:02:33.000 --> 01:02:37.000
If an ungrateful partner

01:02:37.000 --> 01:02:41.000
does not return the debt of the debitor,

01:02:41.000 --> 01:02:45.000
then the factoring company pays for it.

01:02:45.000 --> 01:02:49.000
And then it interacts with the debitor

01:02:49.000 --> 01:02:53.000
to return the money.

01:02:53.000 --> 01:02:57.000
When working with unknown business partners,

01:02:57.000 --> 01:03:01.000
this mechanism is also effective.

01:03:01.000 --> 01:03:05.000
When you are insured and fully guaranteed

01:03:05.000 --> 01:03:09.000
that your money will return to you

01:03:09.000 --> 01:03:13.000
in integrity and safety.

01:03:13.000 --> 01:03:17.000
But it should be emphasized

01:03:17.000 --> 01:03:21.000
that the return of the debt of the debitor

01:03:21.000 --> 01:03:25.000
